  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Sign Of Virtue Complete
---
Confucius said, "This gentleman is a sage. It's just that I've been
tardy and haven't gone to see him yet. But if I go to him as my
teacher, how much more should those who are not my equals! Why only the
state of Lu? I'll bring the whole world along and we'll all become his
followers!"
